name: SILENCIO
description:
/
Silence

I want my work to express the silence The freedom of contemplating existence by itself 'THAT' that only exists for the sake of existing, it does not seek to be venerated, nor does it know misery.

Silence is the material from which the paths of plenitude are built.

Silence is not solitary because it merges in what it contemplates.

And therefore the dead are never alone, for they are part of the whole.

/
